                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-54-off301 t18120916-54-cd302"></join>, a shoulder of veal, value 15 s. and an aitchbone of beef, value 12 s. 7 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120916-54-victim475" type="victimName">
